I'm a 16 year old who doesn't think George Bush has something in common with Hitler and wants to "take over the world." I actually think we have a nice government. Because you see, no one has any real problems with the government until they make them. Nothing has happened to these dumb kids to make the government seem bad, they just find shit to complain about to fit in.

But I am going off topic.

Quit being pussies, I am always right, you are always wrong, IDK.
